text: TAKE ANOTHER LOOK!!! Charming Three-Bedroom Home in the Chesterfield Neighborhood with NO HOA!!! Welcome to this delightful three-bedroom, two-bathroom older home nestled in the heart of Central Phoenix. With a generous 1, 079 square feet of living space, this property offers a perfect blend of vintage charm and modern convenience, including laminate wood flooring, ceiling fans, an eat-in kitchen with a gas range and lots of natural light. As you step inside, you'll find a warm and inviting atmosphere. Seller has added fiber optic cable, making this ideal for a working-at-home owner. This home is perfect for gatherings due to the expansive backyard and east-facing covered patio, providing plenty of room for outdoor activities and gardening enthusiasts. Imagine cultivating your own raised garden beds or even chickens in the already existing chicken coop for fresh eggs right at home. The backyard also has the potential for a refreshing pool or a cozy Casita, making it an ideal space for entertaining or enjoying quiet evenings under the stars. Centrally located, this home is conveniently situated near the light rail, allowing for easy access to all that Phoenix has to offerfrom vibrant downtown dining and entertainment to beautiful parks and recreational areas. Don't miss the opportunity to make this charming Central Phoenix home your own!

text: Look no further than this neat as a pin 4 bd home in Central Phoenix. Featuring an updated kitchen w/ a gas range, granite countertops w/ breakfast bar & large wall pantry. The large living room has a slider to covered back patio where you can lounge in the shade or jump into your pool on a hot day. When those cooler days creep back in, the spa provides for year round fun. Murals decorate the block wall that keeps the fun inside the entertainers space. The bedrooms are a nice size w/ the primary large enough for a king sized bed. The primary also features end-to-end wall closets. This 1959 built house has been updated and maintained - You won't be disappointed. Additional features: Trane A/C unit, dual paned windows, inside laundry, gas cooking, large living areas, dreamy backyard!

text: This charming 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom home is nestled in the desirable Bonnie Lea neighborhood, at the end of a quiet cul-de-sac. Situated on a generous 11, 722 square foot, pie-shaped lot, it offers a large backyard with lush landscaping and flood irrigation - perfect for creating your dream garden. The property also includes an RV gate, a 1-car garage, tile and laminate flooring, an interior laundry room, a formal dining area, and a spacious living/family room. Freshly painted inside and out, this home is centrally located just minutes from Downtown Phoenix, Sky Harbor Airport, I-17, the Light Rail, medical centers, and Grand Canyon University. The Bonnie Lea neighborhood is evolving while preserving its historic charm, offering a timeless and tranquil feel. This is a unique opportunity in a character-rich neighborhood featuring a community garden and a scenic landscaped canal. The house is part of the Westown Neighborhood Community, which organizes community yard sales, get-togethers, and barbecues. Additionally, a few streets in the area are currently undergoing the historical landmark designation process.

text: Spacious, bright, and full of charm! This inviting home sits on a desirable corner lot and offers a generously sized backyard with mature landscaping. Inside, you'll find ceiling fans throughout, stylish tile flooring, and energy-efficient dual pane windows. The updated kitchen features sleek stainless steel appliances, and both bathrooms have been tastefully updated. A brand-new AC unit was installed in 2024 for year-round comfort. The one-car garage offers convenient access to the kitchen and includes a dedicated storage area with a workbench. Enjoy outdoor living under the large covered patio. Ideally located just north of Missouri with easy access to the I-17, this home is nestled in a quiet, centrally located neighborhood close to shopping and dining. No HOA!

text: Beautifully Updated 1940s Brick Ranch in North Encanto Historic District. Thoughtfully modernized while preserving its original charm, this 1940s brick ranch home is nestled in the highly sought-after North Encanto Historic District. Featuring a resort-style pool and patio, this home has been enhanced with hand-scraped bamboo flooring throughout, upgraded dual-pane windows, a stylishly remodeled kitchen with contemporary appliances, and refreshed bathrooms with elegant cement tile. Historic character remains intact with exposed brick walls, adding warmth and texture. The reconfigured floor plan enhances functionality, now offering a spacious primary ensuite and a seamless indoor-outdoor flow. A one-car garage with an attached pergola provides secure parking for two vehicles. The robust Trane HVAC system ensures comfort during the summer months. Major renovations completed in 2018 make this home both timeless and move-in ready.

The master suite offers it's own sitting area with two separate closets. The luxurious Master bath has beautiful custom vanities and custom shower. This home is located on a spacious 7, 301 sq ft lot, right off the 17 freeway and less than a quarter mile away from a huge shopping center, Solano Park and the local YMCA

text: Nicely updated, single level townhome in sought after Orangeaire Villas. End unit backs up to green space & has a bright open floor plan. Engineered Hickory wood floors through out. Primary ensuite bedroom with access to back patio, large walk in closet & tiled walk-in shower. Large covered patio provides a year-round space for relaxing & entertaining. Close to shopping, entertainment & access to major freeways. Phoenix tennis center & dog park just north of complex.

text: Beautifully remodeled townhome ready for you to enjoy! Includes newer flooring, HVAC and plumbing. Enter through the double doors to discover an inviting living room featuring wood tile flooring and fresh paint throughout. The dining area has newer sliding glass doors to back patio for seamless indoor-outdoor living. Completely redone chef's kitchen with all new white shaker cabinets, quartz counters & stainless steel appliances including refrigerator and a convenient pantry. In the large primary bedroom, you will have plush carpet, private bathroom w/granite counters , separate vanity and two walk-in closets. The secondary bedrooms include bi-folding closets and fans. Inside laundry w/washer and dryer included. The spacious back patio has an attached pergola and extra storage closet.

text: Discover this stunning Mid Century Ralph Haver Style home, practically new and situated in a prime Central Phoenix location! This beautifully remodeled gem has been updated throughout. The eat-in kitchen boasts modern cabinets, granite countertops, and all stainless-steel appliances. The open floor plan creates a spacious great room feel. This home features 4 bedrooms, including a primary suite with an ensuite bathroom and a huge walk-in closet. The hall bath has also been remodeled with a contemporary design. Freshly painted inside and out, the home includes double pane windows with 2-inch white wood blinds, wood-look floors, new carpet, AC/heating system, water heater, and ceiling fans. The desert landscaping is equipped with a drip system. An oversized laundry room comes with a washer and dryer, offering ample space for storage or additional cabinets. Your pets will love the large backyard with a secure block wall and solid steel gates. The enlarged driveway can easily accommodate 4 cars. Located within the Central Phoenix Corridor, this home is just minutes from the light rail transit system at Osborn/Indian School stations, and close to shopping, restaurants, museums, theatres, and downtown events. With easy freeway access, this home is the perfect choice for superb urban living! Buy this one first and forget all the rest!

text: Tucked away in a peaceful cul-de-sac, this thoughtfully designed red brick mid-century modern home is a rare find. From the custom wall finishes to the warm-toned colored-concrete flooring, every detail exudes elegance and comfort. Expansive windows fill the space with natural light, enhancing the home's inviting ambiance, while owned solar and newer A/C provide energy efficiency. The beautifully updated kitchen features sleek quartz countertops, a striking mosaic backsplash, modern cabinetry, a spacious pantry, and high-end GE Profile stainless steel appliancesperfectly complemented by a charming breakfast bar. The primary bedroom offers a private retreat with its own en suite bathroom. Step outside to the breathtaking park-like backyard, complete with a paver patio, lush artificial turf, mature landscaping, and enchanting bistro string lighting. Ideally located within walking distance to the light rail and just minutes from Phoenix College, Encanto Park, schools, entertainment and freeway access, this home offers both tranquility and convenience that you won't want to miss!

text: Dream Home at Dream Price in Midtown Phoenix - Move-In Ready & Packed with Potential! This all-brick Bungalow in the desirable ''Piccadilly Park'' combines mid-century character with fresh modern comfort. The solid all-brick construction and a HVAC system new in 2021 offers this home lasting energy efficiency and year-round comfort. text: Stunning modern 3bd/2ba remodel with designer pool in prime Midtown Phoenix. This high-end designed smart home features UPDATED kitchen and baths, charcoal 12x24 tile, exposed sandblasted block walls, quartz countertops, and glass subway backsplash. Includes GE gas cooktop, LG fridge, Nest thermostat, Kraus sink, Kohler fixtures, California Closets, and built-in systems. New windows, electrical, custom steel gates, sleek landscaping, irrigation, and flush shower floors with glass splash guards. Not a flipevery detail carefully crafted. Custom shade trellis looking out to the gorgeous pool with waterfall and matching sandblasted block storage unit complete this one-of-a-kind home. VERY METICULOUS HOME - Does not disappoint!

text: Come check out this one-of-a-kind, move in ready home! So many details that you have to see for yourself. The primary bedroom is a tranquil retreat with its own ensuite bathroom, complete with a tiled walk-in shower for added luxury. The two remaining bedrooms share a newly upgraded hall bathroom ensuring comfort and convenience. Open the sliding glass door and walk out to your own private covered patio, seating areas, easy-care landscape, newly installed RV gate, new electric water heater in laundry room. Superb location near the I-10, I-17 and Hwy 51. Currently tenant occupied on month-to-month lease. Don't miss out on the chance to own the best house in the neighborhood!

Low maintenance living here, as the grounds are nicely maintained and landscape, with beautiful green-belt areas. The community pool is very generously sized. The gated community is conveniently located near main access roads, the freeway, GCU, shopping, restaurants and more.
